# The scripts in this folder authenticate with Firebase Admin SDK using service
# account JSON files, NOT environment variables. Place key files as follows
# (all are gitignored — never commit):
#
#   <repo-root>/service-account.json       — PROD key (used by export script)
#   <repo-root>/dev-service-account.json   — DEV key  (used by seed script)
#   scripts/serviceAccountKey.json         — fallback location (also gitignored)
#
# Safety:
#   - exportFirestore.js refuses to run without the prod key
#   - seedFirestore.js refuses to run without the dev key AND requires the
#     target Firestore to be empty
#
# See README.md "Export & Seed Firestore" section for full instructions.
